Declares RDF storage specific classes.

          Description

Interface Summary
ResultSet Defines the result for a SPARQL select query.
SparqlEndPoint Endpoint to access to the SPARQL interface.
TripleStorage Defines the triples storage.
TripleStorageConfig Defines the configuration for a TripleStorage implementation.
TripleStorageFactory Defines a factory for TripleStorage instances.
TripleStorageFilter Defines the filter for a triple storage.
